// shop-weapon.ipt
// =====================================================================
// A PF2e weaponsmith / arms dealer. Reuses people, customers, prices.
// Entry table: [@WeaponShop]
//
// Prices in COPPER (1 gp = 100 cp), from PF2e Core weapon tables
// where confident; (~) marks approximations to verify.

Title: Weapon Shop
Use: people.ipt
Use: customers.ipt
Use: prices.ipt
Use: stock-count.ipt
Use: items-weapons.ipt

// Optional inputs from a caller (e.g. Town Forge via the API's
// promptValues). Defaults keep the file working standalone.
//   prompt1 town  /  prompt2 shopType (display)  /  prompt3 shopName
Prompt: town {} an unnamed town
Prompt: shopType {} weapons
Prompt: shopName {}
Prompt: size {} town
Prompt: keeperName {}
Prompt: keeperRace {}
Prompt: keeperGender {}
Prompt: keeperAge {}
Prompt: keeperDesc {}
Prompt: custName {}
Prompt: custRace {}
Prompt: custDesc {}

Table: TF-WeaponShop
Set: town={$prompt1}
Set: passedName={$prompt3}
Set: m=[@Markup]
Set: owner=[when]{$prompt5}=[do][@PersonName][else]{$prompt5}[end]
Set: oanc=[when]{$prompt6}=[do][@Ancestry][else]{$prompt6}[end]
Set: odesc=[when]{$prompt9}=[do][@PersonDesc][else]{$prompt9}[end]
**[@WeaponTitle]** *(weapons in {$town})*\n&
**Proprietor:** {$owner}, a {$odesc} {$oanc} who is [@Personality].\n&
**Prices:** {$markupReason}.\n&
**Rack:**\n&
[@WeaponStock]\n&
**{$owner} says:** "[@WeaponQuote]"\n&
**Also here:** [@Customer]

// Caller-supplied name if given, else roll. Prefixed to avoid collision.
Table: WeaponTitle
[when]{$passedName}=[do][@WeaponShopName][else]{$passedName}[end]

Table: WeaponShopName
The [@WpnAdj] [@WpnNoun]
The [@WpnAdj] [@WpnNoun]
[@WpnNoun] & [@WpnNoun]
[@FamilyName]'s [@WpnNoun]
[@FamilyName]'s [@WpnNoun]
The [@WpnNoun] & [@WpnNoun]
[@WpnNoun] and [@WpnNoun]
The [@WpnFixed]

Table: WpnAdj
Keen
Bloodied
Sharp
Iron
Steel
Tempered
Notched
Whetted
Honed
Brazen
Last
Bright
Grim
Battle-Worn
Trusty
Forged
Red
Cold
Sure
Proven

Table: WpnNoun
Edge
Whetstone
Anvil
Blade
Hilt
Pommel
Quillon
Forge
Armoury
Steel
Point
Cut
Hammer
Spear
Axe
Bowstring
Quiver
Scabbard
Crucible
War-Hall

Table: WpnFixed
Keen Edge
Bloodied Anvil
Last Word
Two-Handed Tom's
Sharp Bargain
Edge & Haft
Whetstone
Soldier's Friend

Table: WeaponStock
{!n=={[@StockCount with {$prompt4}]}}[@{$n} WeaponItemLine]

// PF2e Core weapon prices (copper).
Table: WeaponItemLine
[@WeaponItem]\n

Table: WeaponItem
[@PF2eWeapon with {$prompt4}]

Table: WeaponQuote
Balance is everything. Heft it before you buy it.
A dull blade's just a heavy stick, friend.
That one's seen blood. Priced to reflect it.
I sharpen free for a week after purchase.
Don't point it at me unless you mean to pay for it.
Steel doesn't lie, and neither do I.
You want pretty, go to the jeweller. You want deadly, stay here.
Every weapon here will outlive the fool who underestimates it.
